}
─────────────────────────────────────

✅ Done! No other changes needed.
```

## File Organization

```
src/backend/
├── interfaces/          ◄─── Contracts (what every backend must do)
│   ├── IBackendProvider.ts
│   ├── IAuthProvider.ts
│   ├── IDatabase.ts
│   └── IStorage.ts
│
├── config/              ◄─── Generic config system
